# Note: These should be applied by the project owner.

--- server/src/utils/executor.ts (Hypothetical)
- exec(command)
+ execFile(command, args, { shell: false }) // Prevention of command injection

--- src/components/SkillRenderer.tsx (Hypothetical)
- <div dangerouslySetInnerHTML={{ __html: content }} />
